arm_group.description:
The CIP will contain programmatic, structural, and psychosocial components, including:
use of a clinical algorithm by providers;
identification of HIV-infected family members eligible for IPT, using an ICAP-developed family care enrollment form;
review of monitoring data on IPT initiation and adherence during monthly multidisciplinary team meetings;
reimbursement of transportation costs for monthly clinic visits; and
real-time adherence support using IVR via mobile phones and trained Peer Educators.

